selftext:
got referred to, assessed &amp; recommended PHP or residential by a treatment center 1.5 weeks ago, no diagnosis. but my own insurance wants to assess me before agreeing to cover anything higher than their own program, which is just having a team and weekly sessions.

 I moved back home today &amp; bc of my parents and possibly returning hunger, I can't maintain this LW &gt;!low 16s BMI which personally is destructive on my body!&lt; 

 I'm scared I'll gain weight before the insurance assessment, get put in a low level of care as a result, never really get the mental treatment I need, and then return to college &amp; relapse. *I* know that weight doesn't define the severity of an ED but I don't trust others to know. Im so tired of mental health professionals letting me down I just don't know what else to do
